<num value="20000">二萬</num>人</measure>
<pc>，</pc>少者<measure quantity="10000" unit="people">
<num value="10000">萬</num>人</measure>
<pc>，</pc>各為營以拒賊<pc>；</pc>及郭<pc>、</pc>李軍至<pc>，</pc>爭出自效<pc>。</pc>
<num value="37">庚子</num>
<pc>，</pc>攻趙郡<pc>；</pc>
<measure quantity="1" unit="day">
<num value="1">一</num>日</measure>
